[02/04/2019 06:03:22] <font color="#0000ff">...amor.</font>
[02/04/2019 06:03:22] <font color="#ffffff">Muchas gracias.</font>
[02/04/2019 06:03:30] <font color="#0000ff">Cuando calienta el sol.</font>
